Package com.software.fitness_system.instructor_controllers

Class Program

java.lang.Object
com.software.fitness_system.instructor_controllers.Program
public class Program extends Object
It represents a program that can be created to be added into the list of Fitness programs. This Program has attributes for program name, duration, level, goal,price, schedule type, links along with end time.
Author:
Ammar Shafii
